notes: AD8 is an eight-item informant interview

description: AD8 1. Does your family member have problems with judgment (problems making decisions, bad financial decisions, problems with thinking, etc.)?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 2. Does your family member show less interest in hobbies/activities?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 3. Does your family member repeat the same things over and over (questions, stories, or statements)?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 4. Does your family member have trouble learning how to use a tool, appliance, or gadget (e.g., VCR, computer, microwave, remote control)?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 5. Does your family member forget the correct month or year?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 6. Does your family member have trouble handling complicated financial affairs (balancing checkbook, income taxes, paying bills, etc.)?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 7. Does your family member have trouble remembering appointments?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know

description: AD8 8. Does your family member have daily problems with thinking or memory?
coding: 0 = No, no change; 1 = Yes, a change; 2 = NA, don't know
